'''Eanix''' was a North American team.

== History ==
'''Eanix''' was announced on May 23 as the new brand owning the [[NA Challenger Series/2016 Season/Summer Season|NACS 2016 Summer Season]] seed that previously belonged to [[Team Dragon Knights]], after that team was [[List of Competitive Rulings|banned]] from ownership of a team competing in a Riot-sanctioned tournament.<ref name="formation">[http://www.thescoreesports.com/lol/news/7988 Eanix acquires Team Dragon Knights' NACS spot] ''thescoreesports.com''</ref> At the time of announcement, no roster was given.

